    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚总理为澳航免费升舱进行辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/australia-s-prime-minister-defends-free-qantas-flight-upgrades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯 (Anthony Albanese) 面临压力，要求他解释他与澳洲航空有限公司 (Qantas Airways Ltd.) 的关系，此前有指控称他收受了十多次免费航班升舱，其中至少有几次是直接从前老板艾伦·乔伊斯 (Alan Joyce) 那里索取的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/australia-s-prime-minister-defends-free-qantas-flight-upgrades</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 23:54:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元因日本大选结果走软、油价暴跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本执政联盟未能赢得议会多数席位后，日元下跌，引发外界猜测政治不确定性将影响央行的加息政策。以色列袭击伊朗石油设施后，原油价格暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 22:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元下跌，日本股市上涨，因交易员权衡选举影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-weakens-japan-stocks-face-pressure-on-election-blow-to-ldp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者考虑自民党及其联盟伙伴失去多数席位的后果，周一日元下跌 1%，而日本股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-weakens-japan-stocks-face-pressure-on-election-blow-to-ldp</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 21:17:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
